drug.name: Trebananib
drug.description: Trebananib is under investigation for the treatment of Ovarian Cancer, Peritoneal Cancer, and Fallopian Tube Cancer. Trebananib has been investigated for the treatment of Cancer, Oncology, Carcinoma, Metastases, and Colon Cancer, among others.

drug-interaction.description: The risk or severity of Thrombosis can be increased when Darbepoetin alfa is combined with Trebananib.
